{"item_id":"51933aa53e:0","text":"RenderMan for Maya 提供自己的 Shelf，其中包含该插件许多基础且常用功能的快捷方式。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:1","text":"Rendering（渲染）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:2","text":"按钮"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:3","text":"菜单"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:4","text":"说明"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:5","text":"Start 一次预览渲染。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:6","text":"Start 交互式预览渲染。选择要从哪台摄像机进行渲染。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:7","text":"也可以只渲染选中的对象（此选择同样适用于"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:8","text":"预览渲染）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:9","text":"打开"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:10","text":"Image Tool"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:11","text":"，即 'It'"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:12","text":"打开 Localqueue 渲染管理器"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:13","text":"Lighting（灯光）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:14","text":"按钮"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:15","text":"菜单"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:16","text":"说明"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:17","text":"创建新的"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:18","text":"灯光"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:19","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:20","text":"Auto-place lights 可在选中的对象处创建灯光"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:21","text":"即在视口中的对象位置创建，而不是在原点创建。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:22","text":"创建新的"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:23","text":"穹顶灯"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:24","text":"门户灯"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:25","text":"或"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:26","text":"日光灯"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:27","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:28","text":"将选中的几何体转换为"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:29","text":"网格灯光"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:30","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:31","text":"创建一个"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:32","text":"灯光滤镜"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:33","text":"并将其附加到选中的灯光"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:34","text":"Shading（着色）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:35","text":"按钮"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:36","text":"菜单"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:37","text":"说明"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:38","text":"创建一个表面并将其附加到选中的几何体"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:39","text":"创建一个"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:40","text":"PxrVolume"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:41","text":"或 OpenVDB Visualizer。"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:42","text":"从选中的几何体创建遮挡保留"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:43","text":"Stylized Looks"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:44","text":"Archive / Texture / Statistics（归档 / 纹理 / 统计）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:45","text":"按钮"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:46","text":"菜单"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:47","text":"说明"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:48","text":"创建 RenderMan Archive"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:49","text":"打开 Dynamic Shader Binding editor（动态着色器绑定编辑器）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:50","text":"打开 Texture Manager"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:51","text":"打开"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:52","text":"Preset Browser"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:53","text":"Live Statistics"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:54","text":"查看上次渲染的统计信息"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:55","text":"Plugin / Help（插件 / 帮助）"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:56","text":"按钮"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:57","text":"菜单"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:58","text":"说明"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:59","text":"加载 RenderMan for Maya plug-in"}
{"item_id":"51933aa53e:60","text":"在网页浏览器中打开 RenderMan 文档"}
